{{wikipediapar|Peeping Tom}}

==English==

===Etymology===
From [[Peeping Tom]], a [[tailor]] in the legend of [[Lady Godvida]] who watched Godvida riding naked.

===Noun===
'''[[peeping]] [[tom]]''' (''plural'': '''peeping toms''')
#A [[person]] who [[watch]]es another without [[permission]] in a place where the other believes that they have [[privacy]]; a [[voyeur]]